 Last time, that guy brought Jeong Ha Eun to the hospital in his arms. 

24
00:01:35,130 --> 00:01:36,880
What are you talking about?

25
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,150
I'm asking what you're talking about.

26
00:01:42,030 --> 00:01:48,150
The truth is when you came to the emergency room, it was a different person, not Detective Cha.

27
