00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,760
Please just tell us one thing!

144
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,950
 Is Gong Ji Cheol the murderer? 

145
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:30,020
 Please tell us! 

146
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,130
 Is he the real killer? 

147
00:12:31,130 --> 00:12:32,230
 One word, please! 

